      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHOTGUN SEAT (1) had been racing well without winning, recording six minors on end before copping a check in the run and finishing seventh in a Maiden at Cannington (31.28). Can find winning form here. TERRA FIRMA (4) wasn't far away at the finish when 4th and beaten only 3.5 lengths (28.40) at this track. Yet to score from this box but has never missed the frame in two starts. A big run wouldn't surprise. TITAN ATLAS (8) has hit the frame here at the last two runs, most recently finishing third beaten 3 lengths (28.39). Well placed and gets his chance. WISDOM GODDESS (7) is worth some thought after placing at this track and distance last start.",
